    "title": "Senior Software Engineer - ABB India - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at ABB India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Software Engineer to strengthen our Bhubaneswar-based team.\n\nAbout ABB India:\nABB India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in AWS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ABB India!",
